00377 static void rna_trackingMarker_frame_set(PointerRNA *ptr, int value)
00378 {
00379     MovieClip *clip = (MovieClip *) ptr->id.data;
00380     MovieTracking *tracking = &clip->tracking;
00381     MovieTrackingTrack *track;
00382     MovieTrackingMarker *marker = (MovieTrackingMarker *) ptr->data;
00383 
00384     track = tracking->tracks.first;
00385     while (track) {
00386         if (marker >= track->markers && marker < track->markers+track->markersnr) {
00387             break;
00388         }
00389 
00390         track = track->next;

00392 
00393     if (track) {
00394         MovieTrackingMarker new_marker = *marker;
00395         new_marker.framenr = value;
00396 
00397         BKE_tracking_delete_marker(track, marker->framenr);
00398         BKE_tracking_insert_marker(track, &new_marker);
00399     }
00400 }
